refProp.description: Key of the prop that should be used to access element ref
refProp.description_zh: 应该用于访问元素 ref 的 prop 的键

targetType.description:
Determines which events should be handled by the target element.
button target type handles Space and Enter keys to toggle dropdown opened state.
input by default.
targetType.description_zh:
确定目标元素应处理哪些事件。
按钮目标类型处理 Space 和 Enter 键以切换下拉列表打开状态。
input 的 intent 值。

withAriaAttributes.description: Determines whether the target should have aria- attributes, true by default
withAriaAttributes.description_zh: 确定目标是否应具有 aria- 属性，默认为 true

withExpandedAttribute.description: Determines whether the target should have aria-expanded attribute, false by default
withExpandedAttribute.description_zh: 确定目标是否应具有 aria-expanded 属性，默认情况下为 false

withKeyboardNavigation.description: Determines whether component should respond to keyboard events, true by default
withKeyboardNavigation.description_zh: 确定组件是否应响应键盘事件，默认为 true
